Module edu.ntnu.idatt1002.team20
Package edu.ntnu.idatt1002.team20.models.debt

Class Debt

java.lang.Object
edu.ntnu.idatt1002.team20.models.debt.Debt
public class Debt extends Object
Class for the Debt object. Represents a debt registered by the user. Includes methods for getting and setting the debt type, total amount, amount paid and interest rate, as well as a method for showing the progress of the debt through a progress bar.
